    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1 配電系統設計 <br>2 基本觀念 <br>3 電壓與電流計算 <br>4 短路電流計算<br>5 過電流保護協調 <br>6 過電流保護與系統接地<br>7 功因之改善",
        "en": "1. Distribution system design<br>2. Basic concept<br>3. Calculation of voltage drop<br>4. Short-circuit current calculation<br>5. Protection coordination<br>6. Grounding system<br>7. Improvement factor of success rate"
